  "category": "epic_boon",
  "description": "You gain the following benefits.\n\nAbility Score Increase. Increase your Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 30.\n\nFree Casting. Whenever you cast a spell with a level 1\u20134 spell slot, roll [[/r 1d4]]. If the number you roll is the same as the slot's level, the slot isn't expended.\n\nFoundry Note\n\nIf the number is the same, uncheck the Consumption option when using the spell.",
